race.comment: POWER OF THE BRAVE (1) tough gelding who will appreciate a bit of sting out of the ground tonight. Anchored with the 59.5kg when gripped on late for a sound sixth over 1100m at this track. Stanley's 3kg claim will help again and doesn't have to improve much to win this. SHELSTEIN (7) comes down from Queensland and looks up to this stronger contest. Wasn't asked to do much when fifth over 900m in a tick-over trial at Canterbury. Genuine each-way player. COLUMBIA BLUE (8) lightly raced gelding who was heavily supported on resumption when a dominant C1 winner over 1100m at Wyong. Well placed with the claim and proven in all conditions. Each-way. EXTRAVAGENT LAD (3) close to a win and well suited with a bit of sting out of the ground. Back in grade after launching late with a narrow second over 1100m at this track. Keep safe.
